<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 14:07:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>南非政府是哈马斯和伊朗毫无歉意、无耻的代理人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/south-africas-government-is-an-unapologetic-shameless-proxy-for-hamas-and-iran/0000018b-d7d9-dffa-adef-f7d979970000</link><description>政府部长和哈马斯领导人之间的色情、阿谀奉承的恋情，对伊朗的热烈拥抱，明确呼吁攻击犹太人、我们的家园、我们的工作场所、我们的学校。我们南非犹太人想知道我们自己的政府是否正在煽动针对我们的大屠杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:51:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-16/ty-article-opinion/.premium/south-africas-government-is-an-unapologetic-shameless-proxy-for-hamas-and-iran/0000018b-d7d9-dffa-adef-f7d979970000</guid></item><item><title>埃里温犹太教堂在亚美尼亚武装组织反犹太主义袭击中纵火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/yerevan-synagogue-set-on-fire-in-antisemitic-attack-by-armenian-militant-group/0000018b-d7ed-d423-affb-f7efb5d90000</link><description>据称，这次袭击是为了声援巴勒斯坦和黎巴嫩反对犹太复国主义的抵抗运动。该武装组织表示指责以色列支持阿塞拜疆，阿塞拜疆被指控对纳戈尔诺-卡拉巴赫的亚美尼亚人犯下战争罪</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:39:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/yerevan-synagogue-set-on-fire-in-antisemitic-attack-by-armenian-militant-group/0000018b-d7ed-d423-affb-f7efb5d90000</guid></item><item><title>拜登高级官员对约旦河西岸可能爆发另一条战线表示担忧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-express-concern-about-possible-eruption-of-another-front-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-d79f-d423-affb-f7bf32040000</link><description>随着以色列继续对加沙进行地面入侵，美国官员担心约旦河西岸的相对平静可能很快演变成一场全面战争 — — 这是美国和以色列在政治上都无法承受的</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 13:05:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-officials-express-concern-about-possible-eruption-of-another-front-in-the-west-bank/0000018b-d79f-d423-affb-f7bf32040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争结束后，本·拉登为 9/11 所做的辩护在 TikTok 上疯传</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/bin-ladens-justification-for-9-11-goes-viral-on-tiktok-in-wake-of-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-d80f-df9a-ab8b-decf2c9c0000</link><description>这封信周三疯传后，《卫报》将其从网站上删除</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/bin-ladens-justification-for-9-11-goes-viral-on-tiktok-in-wake-of-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-d80f-df9a-ab8b-decf2c9c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的两国解决方案目前不可行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/a-two-state-solution-to-the-israel-palestine-conflict-is-currently-unviable/0000018b-d76b-dffa-adef-f76b885b0000</link><description>10月7日事件发生后，两国模式被视为幻想，同时也成为许多争论的话题。但在不久的将来的某个时刻，人们将会认识到当前的情况是不可持续的。那时这个想法将真正卷土重来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:51:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/a-two-state-solution-to-the-israel-palestine-conflict-is-currently-unviable/0000018b-d76b-dffa-adef-f76b885b0000</guid></item><item><title>雷吉娜·斯佩克托：“许多像我一样的犹太人仍然处于震惊和悲伤之中”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/regina-spektor-many-jews-like-me-are-still-in-shock-and-sorrow/0000018b-d790-dffa-adef-f790f2900000</link><description>这位犹太裔美国歌手对 10 月 7 日之后反犹太主义的兴起感到惊讶，并发现自己从那时起就在社交媒体上争论不休。她对她的英雄尤其失望，其中包括冰岛音乐家比约克，他们对哈马斯的残酷袭击做出了反应。 “感觉就像喝下水道的水，”她告诉《国土报》</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:25:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/regina-spektor-many-jews-like-me-are-still-in-shock-and-sorrow/0000018b-d790-dffa-adef-f790f2900000</guid></item><item><title>自加沙战争爆发以来，进步民主党首次发起阻止美国向以色列出售武器的行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/progressive-democrats-launch-first-effort-to-block-arms-sales-to-israel-since-gaza-war/0000018b-d7be-d423-affb-f7bf71070000</link><description>众议员伊尔汗·奥马尔领导的反对决议呼吁阻止向以色列转让价值 3.2 亿美元的精确制导炸弹设备，因为以色列与哈马斯的战争已接近第七周</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:07:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/progressive-democrats-launch-first-effort-to-block-arms-sales-to-israel-since-gaza-war/0000018b-d7be-d423-affb-f7bf71070000</guid></item><item><title>新民意调查显示，美国犹太选民绝大多数支持拜登处理以色列-加沙战争的方式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-jewish-voters-overwhelmingly-back-bidens-handling-of-israel-gaza-war-new-poll-shows/0000018b-d7ef-dffa-adef-f7effc400000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来首次对美国犹太选民进行的民意调查显示，74% 的人支持拜登在以色列和加沙问题上的做法 ■ 犹太选民对拜登在打击反犹太主义方面的信任程度远远超过特朗普 ■ 68% 的人支持拜登而非特朗普</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 12:05:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/u-s-jewish-voters-overwhelmingly-back-bidens-handling-of-israel-gaza-war-new-poll-shows/0000018b-d7ef-dffa-adef-f7effc400000</guid></item><item><title>难以忽视的事实是以色列将不得不重建加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/the-inconvenient-truth-is-that-israel-will-have-to-rebuild-gaza/0000018b-d7e4-dffa-adef-f7e4f0ec0000</link><description>必须有人对飞地负责，而以色列是唯一现实的候选人。这是一项不受欢迎但必要的任务</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 11:40:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/the-inconvenient-truth-is-that-israel-will-have-to-rebuild-gaza/0000018b-d7e4-dffa-adef-f7e4f0ec0000</guid></item><item><title>在战争时期，以色列的极端正统派为世俗犹太人提供了一座桥梁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-time-of-war-israels-ultra-orthodox-offer-a-bridge-to-secular-jews/0000018b-d794-d423-affb-f7b714900000</link><description>哈马斯史无前例的屠杀引发了一些人的反思，并改变了正统社会对服兵役的看法。目前，许多人正在志愿帮助撤离人员和士兵做出贡献</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 11:06:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/in-time-of-war-israels-ultra-orthodox-offer-a-bridge-to-secular-jews/0000018b-d794-d423-affb-f7b714900000</guid></item><item><title>新理论声称，耶路撒冷失落的圣经纪念碑清晰可见</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-16/ty-article/lost-biblical-monument-in-jerusalem-is-in-plain-sight-new-theory-claims/0000018b-d20c-dffa-adef-f60ce9be0000</link><description>研究表明，耶路撒冷基训泉周围的巨大防御工事可能是圣经中所罗门建造的神秘的“米洛”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:56:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-16/ty-article/lost-biblical-monument-in-jerusalem-is-in-plain-sight-new-theory-claims/0000018b-d20c-dffa-adef-f60ce9be0000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼 MK 被任命代表政府参加有争议的司法小组</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-tapped-to-represent-government-in-disputed-judicial-panel/0000018b-d787-df9a-ab8b-dfcf75d40000</link><description>宗教犹太复国主义议员奥里特·斯特罗克 (Orit Strock) 在周四的委员会会议之前当选，这是自 2022 年底政府成立以来的第一次会议。司法部长亚里夫·莱文 (Yariv Levin) 在向高等法院提出请愿后决定召开该委员会会议，寻求迫使他这样做所以</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/far-right-mk-tapped-to-represent-government-in-disputed-judicial-panel/0000018b-d787-df9a-ab8b-dfcf75d40000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后，十月份寻求枪支许可证的以色列人急剧增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/dramatic-increase-in-israelis-seeking-gun-permits-in-october-following-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d4db-d423-affb-f7fb34610000</link><description>国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔强调公民防卫工作的必要性，敦促任何有资格的人“即使在今天也要这样做”；其他人则警告大规模分发枪支的后果</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:11:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/dramatic-increase-in-israelis-seeking-gun-permits-in-october-following-hamas-massacre/0000018b-d4db-d423-affb-f7fb34610000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯大屠杀后失踪的 12 岁以色列女孩的家人放弃希望，告别</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/giving-up-hope-family-of-girl-12-missing-since-massacre-say-goodbye/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb37350000</link><description>来自贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 的 12 岁女孩 Liel Hetzroni 的家人决定将她的物品埋在尸体的地方。 “莉尔被谋杀的事实很清楚，”一位亲戚在向莉尔告别时说道，莉尔被认为已经死亡，旁边还有她的双胞胎兄弟、阿姨和祖父，他们都于 10 月 7 日被杀。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:04:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/giving-up-hope-family-of-girl-12-missing-since-massacre-say-goodbye/0000018b-d4db-df9a-ab8b-dedb37350000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷附近检查站发生枪击事件，六名以色列人受伤，其中一人伤势严重；三名枪手被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/6-wounded-1-critically-in-shooting-attack-at-checkpoint-near-jerusalem-3-gunmen-killed/0000018b-d757-d423-affb-f7f7059b0000</link><description>三名袭击者在伯利恒附近西岸的“隧道”检查站向安全部队开枪。警方报告称，他们打算在耶路撒冷境内发动袭击，但被拦截并向驻扎在那里的警察开枪</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 10:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/6-wounded-1-critically-in-shooting-attack-at-checkpoint-near-jerusalem-3-gunmen-killed/0000018b-d757-d423-affb-f7f7059b0000</guid></item><item><title>“TikTok 明星”：讲俄语的老年人向以色列战争努力伸出援手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tiktok-stars-the-russian-speaking-seniors-lending-a-hand-to-the-israeli-war-effort/0000018b-d3dc-df9a-ab8b-dfdc01250000</link><description>20 多年前从前苏联集团移民到以色列的四名妇女解释了为什么她们不能在加沙战争持续时袖手旁​​观，并感到有责任尽其所能提供帮助</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 08:47:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tiktok-stars-the-russian-speaking-seniors-lending-a-hand-to-the-israeli-war-effort/0000018b-d3dc-df9a-ab8b-dfdc01250000</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会呼吁暂停加沙人道主义行动并无条件释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/un-security-council-calls-for-humanitarian-pauses-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-d6ee-d168-a3ef-d7fe19b50000</link><description>安理会“软化”了这一呼吁的措辞，该呼吁在之前失败的决议中被视为“要求”。美国、英国和俄罗斯投了弃权票</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 07:56:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/un-security-council-calls-for-humanitarian-pauses-unconditional-release-of-hostages/0000018b-d6ee-d168-a3ef-d7fe19b50000</guid></item><item><title>利库德集团“对内塔尼亚胡感到愤怒”，称“政府的日子已经屈指可数了”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/likud-mk-enraged-with-netanyahu-says-governments-days-are-numbered/0000018b-d6db-d423-affb-f7fb86cb0000</link><description>前公共外交部长加利特·迪斯塔尔·阿特巴扬 (Galit Distal Atbaryan) 写道，“我对以色列北部和南部政府统治下崛起的怪物感到愤怒，这让我心碎并让我辞职。”</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 06:53:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/likud-mk-enraged-with-netanyahu-says-governments-days-are-numbered/0000018b-d6db-d423-affb-f7fb86cb0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称在加沙希法发现人质信息；医院院长：军队移走了尸体</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-live/biden-war-wont-end-until-hamas-destroyed-un-calls-for-urgent-cease-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-d5f5-df9a-ab8b-dffd41030000</link><description>以色列国防军公布了两名在加沙战斗中丧生的以色列士兵的名字 ■ 拜登表示，重新占领加沙将是“一个大错误” ■ 八名以色列人在耶路撒冷检查站枪击事件中受伤，其中一人伤势严重 ■ 联合国安理会呼吁“紧急”停火并无条件释放以色列人人质 ■ 以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩真主党 ■ 巴勒斯坦报道：以色列国防军重新进入希法，进行挖掘 ■ 以色列反对派领袖猛烈抨击内塔尼亚胡，提议由另一位利库德集团成员领导新政府 ■ 自 239 年 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵被杀加沙被扣押的人质 ■ 哈马斯控制的卫生部：11,240 人死亡</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 04:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article-live/biden-war-wont-end-until-hamas-destroyed-un-calls-for-urgent-cease-fire-in-gaza/0000018b-d5f5-df9a-ab8b-dffd41030000</guid></item><item><title>警察在民主党总部逮捕要求加沙停火的示威者后，犹太抗议者与亲以色列议员发生争执</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/jewish-protesters-pro-israel-lawmaker-spar-after-gaza-cease-fire-rally/0000018b-d63e-d168-a3ef-d7fe6ae70000</link><description>国会警察暴力驱散了在民主党国会竞选委员会外参加跨宗教守夜活动和反对以色列加沙战争的公民不服从活动的示威者，要求议员支持停火。</description><pubDate>Thu, 16 Nov 2023 04:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-16/ty-article/.premium/jewish-protesters-pro-israel-lawmaker-spar-after-gaza-cease-fire-rally/0000018b-d63e-d168-a3ef-d7fe6ae70000</guid></item></channel></rss>